{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-press-release-tsx","path":"/media-center/experts-strive-for-consensus-on-globalization-during-doha-debates-program","result":{"data":{"contentfulPagePressRelease":{"id":"aff55461-24a8-53bb-af7b-a1a52b8e4e4b","slug":"experts-strive-for-consensus-on-globalization-during-doha-debates-program","title":"Experts Strive for Consensus on Globalization During Doha Debates Program at TEDSummit","date":"2019-07-24","filterTags":null,"filterEntity":[{"contentful_id":"10hg0ZIMpAScy8CyHsPiMl"}],"heroImage":null,"modulesWrapper":[{"modules":[{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"f64d8a46-c892-50ed-8755-cc0fe1f5546a","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Experts from diverse perspectives argued the merits, consequences, and future of globalization in a solutions-focused Doha Debates program today. A production of Qatar Foundation (QF), the debate was held at the TEDSummit 2019 conference in Edinburgh, Scotland.  </p>\n<p>The debate’s participants, with the help of a conflict resolution expert, bridged differences, found common ground, and agreed on recommendations to help ensure globalization benefits all. </p>\n<p>The program included questions and suggestions from audience members in person, as well as millions of people around the world watching the debate via a Twitter livestream.</p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"4f15c1c7-2ee4-524e-bc50-a03e06e07386","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"f098c372-b156-55b2-95c6-e00009a172e0","title":"Image2 DD in Scotland","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":2299,"height":1530}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6ICEZxpO6ZwTy1E3KYoriy/deb810003445e1bcd381a9af93e8b6b6/Image2_DD_in_Scotland.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6ICEZxpO6ZwTy1E3KYoriy/deb810003445e1bcd381a9af93e8b6b6/Image2_DD_in_Scotland.jpg?w=280&h=150&q=85 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6IC